OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson stripped of
OL,4,Cknighthood
OL,6,FFormer Democratic Unionist Party
OL,7,Fleader Jeffrey Donaldson has been
OL,8,Fstripped of his knighthood by the King.
OL,10,FDonaldson, 63, was convicted at Newry
OL,11,FCrown Court last month of 18 sex
OL,12,Foffences between 1985 and 2008,
OL,13,Fincluding one count of rape, relating
OL,14,Fto the abuse of two women when they
OL,15,Fwere children.
OL,17,FThe two victims gave evidence against
OL,18,Fhim during the trial, during which
OL,19,FDonaldson had denied the offences. He
OL,20,Fhas since lodged an appeal of his
OL,21,Fconviction.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
