OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784877490
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson stripped of
OL,4,Cknighthood
OL,6,FIn the aftermath, Donaldson had asked
OL,7,Ffor his name to be removed from the
OL,8,Flist of members of the Privy Council
OL,9,Fand had moved to renounce his
OL,10,Fknighthood.
OL,12,FThe Gazette, one of the UK's official
OL,13,Fjournals of record, confirmed on
OL,14,FThursday that Donaldson's knighthood
OL,15,Fhas been forfeited.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
