OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson stripped of
OL,4,Cknighthood
OL,6,FPublished by the Central Chancery of
OL,7,Fthe Orders of Knighthood, the notice
OL,8,Fstated: "The King has directed the
OL,9,Fcancellation and annulment of the
OL,10,FKnighthood conferred upon Jeffrey Mark
OL,11,FDonaldson on the 11 June 2016 as a
OL,12,FKnight Bachelor."
